Contents of this packaging:

	Hugo Engine           the interpreter
	hc                    the compiler
	hd                    the debugger
	hdhelp.hlp            the help file for the debugger

	Amiga.txt             Amiga porting notes, by David Kinder
	Release.txt           release notes, by Kent Tessman
	Hugo Manual.guide     programming manual, by Kent Tessman
	Manual.txt            programming manual (text only version)

	Games/                
		Spur.hex         a full game to play

	Examples/
		Sample.hug       a sample source code
		Shell.hug        a source code to build on

		hugolib.hug      to create a #linkable version of hugolib.h
		hugolib.txt      a note on precompiling the Hugo library

	Library/   
		changes.txt      Hugo library changes file, by Julian Arnold
           
		hugolib.h        library definitions and routines
		grammar.g        standard grammar definitions

		objlib.h         a library of useful object definitions

		hugofix.h        debugging routines
		hugofix.g        debugging grammar

		verbstub.h       additional verb routines
		verbstub.g       additional verb grammar


